INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS / INSTALLATIONSANLEITUNG
*********************************************************

- If you want to get up and running quickly and easily -
:~/tar -xzvf simurun2-0.x.x.tar.gz
:~/cd simurun2
:~/simurun2/> qmake simurun2.pro
:~/simurun2/> make

As user root / als Benutzer root
:~/simurun2/> make install

or as non-root-user root password is required
oder als normaler Benutzer, dazu wird das root Passwort bemÃ¶tigt
:~/simurun2/> su -c"make install"
password:

